<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٢٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">‌قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/474">‌وَابْنُ السَّرْحِ </a>قَالَا:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٠٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">‌سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">‌الزُّهْرِيِّ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6011">‌مَحْمُودِ بْنِ الرَّبِيعِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3120">‌عُبَادَةَ بْنِ الصَّامِتِ </a>يَبْلُغُ بِهِ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا صَلَاةَ لِمَنْ لَمْ يَقْرَأْ بِفَاتِحَةِ الْكِتَابِ فَصَاعِدًا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ سُفْيَانُ:</span> لِمَنْ يُصَلِّي وَحْدَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>